name: APTITUDE UNLIMITED ( 60 hrs / 225+ Videos )
description: This Course is a collection of 200+ Aptitude Videos (All Topics in Quant & Reasoning) taught by Crisna Chaitanya Reddy & Vamsee Krishna Reddy. These videos cover all topics in aptitude which helps every aspirant to clear Aptitude section in CRT, Bank Exams, SSC, CAT, I-CET, GRE, GATE, RRB, SI/CONSTABLE, VRO/VRA, and many more private and public sector recruitments.
